Full-Service Travel Centers
Serving up the most amenities and respect to highway travelers nationwide.
















Professional Truck Drivers

Ever since we opened for business over 40 years ago, we’ve been providing the best service on the interstate. Each of our locations is designed to deliver maximum customer efficiency And our employees are trained to understand our customer’s needs. It’s no wonder we’re the most trusted brand in the truck stop industry, Voted Best, year-in and year-out.

More about Professional Truck Drivers










Commercial Fleet Accounts

These days, the clock is ticking. New HOS regulations are cutting into the operating efficiency of fleets everywhere. That’s why TA and Petro’s full-service advantage leads to better optimization of a fleet’s business. Your drivers can get fuel, get fed, and even get maintenance all in one stop. Now, that’s operating efficiency that’s Voted Best!

More about Commercial Fleet Accounts










Cars and RVs

Whether you’re on a family vacation or a business trip, with a car full of kids or all by yourself, TA and Petro are your perfect pit stops. From good food, snacks, and gasoline to supplies and gifts, we have it all.

More about Cars and RVs










Tour Bus and Bus Drivers

TA and Petro wants to make your visit as pleasant and relaxing as possible for your group, while understanding your need to stay on a tight schedule. As the largest full-service travel center network, TA and Petro offer many advantages.

More about Tour Bus and Bus Drivers







